Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is going to announce our engagement at the New Year Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Mira likes Kira too, he'll soon be caught by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also definitely be... {\alpha&HFF&}put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also definitely be... put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send me a fan letter than only I will recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, {\alpha&HFF&}include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I receive it, please continue with your judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a fake copy of the notebook and continue your judgments using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are inviting me to do that by wearing such short skirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami is getting off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.99,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(364,363)}Vigilance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who was harassing a girl in the same car as Mikami just collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened a few seconds after Mikami wrote something in the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This probably means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we must first get close to Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to do that, we must be wary of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... {\alpha&HFF&}the existence of the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... the existence of the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Shinigami finds out that we are trailing Mikami, we have to assume that it will warn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only those who've touched the notebook can see the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to avoid something that can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's difficult, please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, Light-kun will meet with Takada in this room again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after the secret meeting began, {\alpha&HFF&}Takada received a phone call from Kira, and the hidden cameras had to be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after the secret meeting began, Takada received a phone call from Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and the hidden cameras had to be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after the secret meeting began, Takada received a phone call from Kira, and the hidden cameras had to be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first thought was that this would allow communication through written messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than the bug attached to me, there's nothing else in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, all that's left is the bathroom then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Light-kun so insistent on the cameras and bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}to begin with, why is Kira allowing this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... to begin with, why is Kira allowing this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't make sense here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any chance they are communicating through written messages... {\alpha&HFF&}what can be done is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by any chance they are communicating through written messages... what can be done is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun. I spoke privately with Amane-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This puts Light-kun in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so happy about, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san said she would announce your engagement at the New Year Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinch! {\alpha&HFF&}Pinch! Big pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinch! Pinch! {\alpha&HFF&}Big pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinch! Pinch! Big pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah no... {\alpha&HFF&}It's just that I haven't been able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah no... It's just that I haven't been able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me there isn't anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Misa... doing such useless things... {\alpha&HFF&}no, Takada is to blame as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Misa... doing such useless things... no, Takada is to blame as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are such unreasonable creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special...? {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special...? I wonder if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one carrying out Kira's judgments before T.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had obtained Kira's power from somewhere that I wasn't aware of, {\alpha&HFF&}and because she knew I was Kira, it couldn't be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had obtained Kira's power from somewhere that I wasn't aware of, and because she knew I was Kira, it couldn't be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had that not been the case, I wouldn't have chosen such an airheaded person like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san was carrying out Kira's judgment... {\alpha&HFF&}but now I am... there was no choice with Amane-san, while I was chosen by Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san was carrying out Kira's judgment... but now I am... {\alpha&HFF&}there was no choice with Amane-san, while I was chosen by Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san was carrying out Kira's judgment... but now I am... there was no choice with Amane-san, {\alpha&HFF&}while I was chosen by Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san was carrying out Kira's judgment... but now I am... there was no choice with Amane-san, while I was chosen by Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, please believe me. {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, there's only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, please believe me. Right now, there's only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's only you"? That doesn't sound like Yagami-kun at all. Such a common line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it doesn't sound like Light-kun. It's just a poor excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... between Amane and Takada, who is he really interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be... {\alpha&HFF&}both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be... both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them!? How can anyone allow that kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's not me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on I'll believe what you say, but if you're lying, the consequences will be heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll tell Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that Kira has become a necessity in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but recently I've been thinking about whether the day that you and I can be together will ever come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another, I hate Kira for choosing Takada-san as his representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's alright to kill evil people, we aren't bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have the right to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for us to become happy, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira must disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for us to become happy, Kira must disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}if only Kira didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... if only Kira didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be done if Kira were to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For us to be happy... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira must be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For us to be happy... Kira must be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, we'll need your cooperation. {\alpha&HFF&}It'll also be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, we'll need your cooperation. It'll also be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that I'll be going against police policy, and you'll be going against Kira and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if it comes to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazingly well put.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If cooperating with you means that we can both be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like Light-kun... a complete turn-around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he was able to change his two-timing relationship with Misa-Misa into cooperation with Taki!
