Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-at-shi-ni-ga-mi-has-n't-a-pp-ea-red-sin-ce-he-ga-ve-me-the-no-{\alpha&HFF&}te-book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-at-shi-ni-ga-mi-has-n't-a-pp-ea-red-sin-ce-he-ga-ve-me-the-no-te-{\alpha&HFF&}book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-at-shi-ni-ga-mi-has-n't-a-pp-ea-red-sin-ce-he-ga-ve-me-the-no-te-book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shinigami hasn't appeared since he gave me the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami was given a notebook by a Shinigami, however, the Shinigami hasn't been with him since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Yagami-kun, will that be all for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over! Today was pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty tough to do this for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't tell by the smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back after I check out of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san has it pretty tough, having to check in and out of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! {\alpha&HFF&}The nail mark that was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! The nail mark that was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of the four notes have no nail marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room is still as it was... {\alpha&HFF&}room service hasn't been in here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room is still as it was... room service hasn't been in here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have the memos been changed to new ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're communicating in writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\alpha&HFF&}You want to see Near? And speak to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want to see Near? {\alpha&HFF&}And speak to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want to see Near? And speak to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, I'm pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being blindfolded, I can't really say things like "pleased to meet you".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't bring any weapons or cameras with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it won't matter if you take off your blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}I believe you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I believe you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is meeting Takada every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have been communicating with notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, {\alpha&HFF&}please do not do needless things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, please do not do needless things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Needless things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the point now where we don't need further proof of Kira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop Kira, it is up to me to expose him, and let him suffer a total defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, I'll be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are already out of the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you still want to capture Kira despite knowing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, {\alpha&HFF&}continue to watch him as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, continue to watch him as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... {\alpha&HFF&}keep watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... keep watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}However, there is reason to keep watching L, and that has been written into my scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. However, there is reason to keep watching L, {\alpha&HFF&}and that has been written into my scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. However, there is reason to keep watching L, and that has been written into my scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can help me this way, {\alpha&HFF&}in order to defeat Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can help me this way, in order to defeat Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, please witness... {\alpha&HFF&}the end of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, please witness... the end of Kira.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This past year has been a dramatic one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the host for this year's New Year Show, Takada Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the New Year Show is finally going to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, come look at the situation with judgments and check the list of deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can wait until the performance of our Misa-Misa, the main act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there is something I must apologize to everyone for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main act for this year, Amane Misa-san, has yet to arrive at the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been no word from Mogi either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me go back to NHN!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do that, Misa will be seen as someone who backs out at the last minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa, please stay calm and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with you, Mochii?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has that got to do with Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We considered using guns to get you to come with us as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't resist at all... {\alpha&HFF&}that really helped us, Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't resist at all... that really helped us, Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've resisted if Aizawa hadn't told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing about the memo pads... {\alpha&HFF&}it really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing about the memo pads... it really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost track of Mogi and Amane Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we've invited them over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, abduction is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mr. Mogi and Amane accepted happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will connect you to them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi-san, {\alpha&HFF&}Misa-san... this is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi-san, Misa-san... {\alpha&HFF&}this is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi-san, Misa-san... this is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you both put yourselves in Near's custody willingly. Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa was opposed to it! But Mochii said that it'd be better to keep quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, everyone will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Since both of you agreed, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane Misa, highly suspected of being the second Kira, is now a captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, you should know the meaning of this move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.32,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing around! You think you can get away with not bringing out Misa-Misa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.66,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Bring her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner and the others seem to have carried it out smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's past 9pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami has a fixed routine and goes home at almost the exact same time every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every Monday and Thursday, he will definitely be at this gym at about 2100 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In the four years he's been a member, he's always maintained this routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't rest, even on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I signed up too, and found that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he should be going this Monday the 31st too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... for a person who'd go even on New Year's Day, New Year's Eve will not be an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible for you to touch the notebook on the 31st in the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can deal with the security in the hotel, and there are no surveillance cameras in the locker room either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is indeed a Shinigami, there's a possibility that I will die, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am getting you to do this in order to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not see a Shinigami after touching it, I will need to observe what happens to determine whether it is following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too afraid, I'll get Lester to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is indeed a Shinigami around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if that's the case, maybe I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I only have to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've succeeded in touching the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time and place, I have not seen a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, please connect me to Mr. Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mogi, according to the rules of the Death Note, how long can someone be manipulated before their death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the data from the Yotsuba Incident, 23 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The killings from the Yotsuba Incident were enough to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, there is a possibility that Gevanni is being controlled to say that a Shinigami is not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrange for a showdown with L after 24 days... {\alpha&HFF&}and we'll carry it out if Gevanni is still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrange for a showdown with L after 24 days... and we'll carry it out if Gevanni is still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:42.97,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(362,394)}January 3rd
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, the New Year's Show must have been hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... to think Amane-san just disappeared like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give T instructions to contact you once he has confirmed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the message comes, give me a call or send me an email, saying "I want to see you as soon as possible".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.66,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(364,395)}January 6th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to see exactly how it was written.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether there were any patterns as he wrote the names, and exactly what kind of notebook it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to see all the details for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Gevanni has done a fantastic job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The handwriting matches that of Mikami's prosecution reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, this was written by Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(524,285)}To be continued
